Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:29.77,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小满…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:32.45,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你昨天没来  我很担心来着哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:35.42,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}果然许愿是许对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:37.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}许愿…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:37.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:41.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我向这星之沙许愿  让美风再回到我身边哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:42.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:45.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好了  吃早饭  吃早饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:47.47,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好耶！ 小满也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:48.93,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你就不知道客套些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:51.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你说什么！ 别这么小气你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.23,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这不是小气！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}早晨怎么没等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.32,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可是接你去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.83,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  稍微有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:32.00,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这到无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:38.06,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个梦… 还在继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:39.02,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.27,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨天晚上  梦到了夜幕下的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.89,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在森林中我和谁在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:45.97,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}森林？ 和谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道  不过有个人陪在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:53.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我便问那个人  海是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:57.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}于是那个人就告诉了我很多关于海的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.15,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}光是说说话就感到很快乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.67,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我简直想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:05.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把那些话放在心中永远珍藏下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.72,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那么高兴的话你就一直睡下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:10.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎  嘎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.82,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}电风扇～　电风扇～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:22.90,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}国崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:24.77,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}人偶表演如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.25,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个… 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.33,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}失败了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.90,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么嘛  国崎往人真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.63,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}干什么你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}闭嘴！ 只知道吃饭的家伙少在这说大话！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.08,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}玩了吃  吃了睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:49.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是让人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:52.94,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨天晚上  我梦见了父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:54.54,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:59.44,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小时候  我经常和父亲一起在这里看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.92,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是关于那时候的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:03.37,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:07.24,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在每颗星星上都住着一位神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.73,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}他们在守护着我们哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:14.01,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}而且  还会将凝望星星的人的心灵净化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:19.75,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后没过多久  父亲就离开了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.73,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妹妹流产了那件事之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:26.02,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}父亲和母亲的关系变得不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.11,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的父亲现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:32.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听说在远方的城镇  和其他的女性再婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.25,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在他离开时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.35,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}父亲就给了我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.34,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐  你不去工作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.16,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}稍微休息休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:49.06,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐  美风现在是离家出走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.58,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:53.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为小满是美风的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.66,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就知道  这样下去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风必须从梦中醒过来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.74,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.80,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小满先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再见了  土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:11.63,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.34,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.61,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.29,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:22.23,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.38,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有什么事请尽管过来不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.21,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.52,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正在回想起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:34.59,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}说是感到失去了什么珍贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.06,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因此就来问诊了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:44.91,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我对她说  终有一天她找到时就会想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:48.39,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剩下的就要看美风了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.51,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.66,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:08.89,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我决定离开这个小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.95,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为在这里逗留的时间太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.75,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是该走的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}跟我一起走吧  远野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:24.13,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想让你看看这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.24,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不再是梦  是真正的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.71,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.16,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一起走吧  去寻找属于我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.03,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.43,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.45,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯… 国崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.95,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}离开小镇前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.63,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想和小满…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.04,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用了  跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.39,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不容易  总算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.29,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.28,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小满说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.78,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不希望看到美风寂寞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.22,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小满她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.69,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}接下来如何选择  就看你自己的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.95,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想的话  真跟我一起去旅行也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.79,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我会带你去个其他什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}选择是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:38.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}按照你  远野美风自己的意志决定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.19,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.30,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:03.95,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.26,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天也是繁星密布呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.29,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.56,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}美风也在看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  也许和她母亲一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:29.46,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小满… 必须要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.77,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.83,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}愿意的话我送你回去哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:38.62,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你家在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.96,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}回去的地方… 是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.05,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小满？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:47.63,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天空中  有一个非常寂寞的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:48.83,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.10,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天空中…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.84,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个女孩总是做着悲伤的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.23,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一遍遍重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:59.02,chs for air往人,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她无法得到幸福  所以只能做着悲伤的梦
